## RULE 9 — emailNotifier.js

FILE: backend/src/scan/modules/emailNotifier.js

PURPOSE: Send a real email via Resend API when a scan completes.

IMPLEMENTATION RULES:
- Only send if: scanConfig.notificationEmail is set AND process.env.RESEND_API_KEY or scanConfig.resendApiKey is set.
- Load the final scan stats and top 5 findings from the database.
- Make a POST request to Resend API:
  URL: https://api.resend.com/emails
  Headers:
    Authorization: Bearer [resend api key]
    Content-Type: application/json
  Body:
    from: "Chain Breaker AI <scan@yourdomain.com>"  (use process.env.RESEND_FROM_EMAIL or "onboarding@resend.dev" as fallback)
    to: [scanConfig.notificationEmail]
    subject: "Chain Breaker AI Scan Complete — [criticalCount] Critical Issues Found on [targetUrl]"
    html: [generate HTML below]

- HTML email template (generate this as a string):
  ```html
  <div style="font-family:sans-serif;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;background:#0a0a0f;color:#f1f0ff;padding:24px;border-radius:12px">
    <h1 style="color:#22d3ee;margin-bottom:4px">Chain Breaker AI Security Scan Complete</h1>
    <p style="color:#9896b0;margin-top:0">Scan completed on [date]</p>
    <div style="background:#111118;border:1px solid #2a2a3a;border-radius:8px;padding:16px;margin:16px 0">
      <p style="margin:4px 0"><strong>Target:</strong> [targetUrl]</p>
      <p style="margin:4px 0"><strong>Duration:</strong> [duration]</p>
      <p style="margin:4px 0"><strong>Total Findings:</strong> [total]</p>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;margin:16px 0">
      <div style="background:#ef444420;border:1px solid #ef4444;border-radius:8px;padding:12px;flex:1;text-align:center">
        <div style="font-size:28px;font-weight:bold;color:#ef4444">[critical]</div>
        <div style="color:#9896b0;font-size:12px">Critical</div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#f9731620;border:1px solid #f97316;border-radius:8px;padding:12px;flex:1;text-align:center">
        <div style="font-size:28px;font-weight:bold;color:#f97316">[high]</div>
        <div style="color:#9896b0;font-size:12px">High</div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#eab30820;border:1px solid #eab308;border-radius:8px;padding:12px;flex:1;text-align:center">
        <div style="font-size:28px;font-weight:bold;color:#eab308">[medium]</div>
        <div style="color:#9896b0;font-size:12px">Medium</div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#22c55e20;border:1px solid #22c55e;border-radius:8px;padding:12px;flex:1;text-align:center">
        <div style="font-size:28px;font-weight:bold;color:#22c55e">[low]</div>
        <div style="color:#9896b0;font-size:12px">Low</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <h3 style="color:#f1f0ff">Top Critical Findings</h3>
    [for each top finding: <div style="border-left:3px solid #ef4444;padding:8px 12px;margin:8px 0;background:#111118"><strong>[title]</strong><br><span style="color:#9896b0;font-size:12px">[url]</span></div>]
    <a href="[reportUrl]" style="display:inline-block;background:#6366f1;color:white;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;margin-top:16px">View Full Report</a>
    <p style="color:#5a5870;font-size:11px;margin-top:24px">Sent by Chain Breaker AI</p>
  </div>
  ```

- Replace all [placeholders] with real values from the scan and findings.
- reportUrl = process.env.FRONTEND_URL + "/scan/" + scanId + "/report"
- If Resend API returns error: log the error but do NOT throw — scan is already complete.
- Export: module.exports = async function sendEmailNotification(scanId, scanConfig, db)

